fields.name: mask
fields.description: Parameters bitmask. Only the masked parameters will be applied.

bits.name: drLim
bits.description: Reserved (apply DR limit settings, only applicable for protocol versions less than 14.00)

bits.name: dgpsMask
bits.description: Apply DGPS settings (not supported for protocol versions less than 13.00)

bits.name: cnoThreshold
bits.description: Apply CNO threshold settings (cnoThresh, cnoThreshNumSvs) (not supported for protocol versions less than 14.00)

bits.name: utc
bits.description: Apply UTC settings (not supported for protocol versions less than 16.00)

fields.name: dynModel
fields.description: Dynamic platform model: 0 = portable, 2 = stationary, 3 = pedestrian, 4 = automotive, 5 = sea, 6 = airborne with <1g acceleration, 7 = airborne with <2g acceleration, 8 = airborne with <4g acceleration, 9 = wrist-worn watch (not supported for protocol versions less than 18.00), 10 = bike (supported for protocol versions 19.20)

values.name: wrist
values.description: wrist-worn watch (not supported for protocol versions less than 18.00)

fields.name: fixMode
fields.description: Position fixing mode: 1 = 2D only, 2 = 3D only, 3 = auto 2D/3D

fields.name: fixedAlt
fields.description: Fixed altitude (mean sea level) for 2D fix mode

fields.name: minElev
fields.description: Minimum elevation for a GNSS satellite to be used in NAV

fields.name: drLimit
fields.description: Reserved (maximum time to perform dead reckoning (linear extrapolation) in case of GPS signal loss, only applicable for protocol versions less than 14.00)

fields.name: dgnssTimeout
fields.description: DGNSS timeout (not supported for protocol versions less than 13.00)

fields.name: cnoThreshNumSVs
fields.description: Number of satellites required to have C/N0 above cnoThresh for a fix to be attempted (not supported for protocol versions less than 14.00)

fields.name: cnoThresh
fields.description: C/N0 threshold for deciding whether to attempt a fix (not supported for protocol versions less than 14.00)

fields.name: staticHoldMaxDist
fields.description: Static hold distance threshold (before quitting static hold) (not supported for protocol versions less than 15.00)

fields.name: utcStandard
fields.description: UTC standard to be used (see the GNSS time bases section in the Integration manual): 0 = Automatic; receiver selects based on GNSS configuration, 3 = UTC as operated by the U.S. Naval Observatory (USNO); derived from GPS time, 5 = UTC as combined from multiple European laboratories; derived from Galileo time, 6 = UTC as operated by the former Soviet Union (SU); derived from GLONASS time, 7 = UTC as operated by the National Time Service Center (NTSC), China; derived from BeiDou time (not supported for protocol versions less than 16.00)

values.name: auto
values.description: Automatic; receiver selects based on GNSS configuration

values.name: utc_gps
values.description: UTC as operated by the U.S. Naval Observatory (USNO); derived from GPS time

values.name: utc_galileo
values.description: UTC as combined from multiple European laboratories; derived from Galileo time

values.name: utc_glonass
values.description: UTC as operated by the former Soviet Union (SU); derived from GLONASS time

values.name: utc_ntsc
values.description: UTC as operated by the National Time Service Center (NTSC)
